title: "Customize Your Workspace"
pageId: "697c70affacf84433851104c"
---

From the **Getting Started** section on the **Docuwiz Dashboard**, click the **Customize Your Workspace** card on the right panel.

Docuwiz redirects you to **Settings → General Settings**, where you can update your workspace details and preferences \(see Figure 1\).

The Customize Your Workspace option allows you to personalize your Docuwiz environment by updating workspace details, branding elements, and theme preferences. You can modify your workspace name, upload a logo and favicon, and select a color theme that aligns with your organization’s branding.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Figure 1: Customize your workspace

For detailed information, see **General Settings** in the **Workspace Settings** section.
